<plot>A dozen sketches: (1) "L'educazione sessuale dei figli" or how it is not easy for parents to reveal the mystery of birth to their young children. (2) "Le adolescenti et l'amore" or how the first kiss can be pleasant for teenagers and a worry to their parents. (3) "La sfregiata" or how violent a male ego can be after a woman's rejection. (4) "La prova d'amore" or how double standards work in view of a woman's loss of virginity. (5) "Le ragazze-madri" or how modern psichology can influence a pregnant woman to deal with her dilemma. (6) "La prima notte" or how hiding her sexual past to the bridegroom does not succeed past their nuptial night. (7) "La frenesia del successo" or how aspiring actresses have to pay a price for success. (8) "L'infideltá coniugale" or how a matrimony can be a social hypocrisy by a cheating couple. (9) "Il matrimonio assurdo" or how a girl eager to marry discovers too late her husband's true nature. (19) "La vedova bianca" or how an emigrant's wife shall overcome her sexual need through music, and dancing. (11) "La separazione legale" or how divorce can be a way to settle peacefully a union that no longer works. (12) "Il prezzo dell'amore" or how a man can overcome the shock of being married to a woman who was raped by some truck drivers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?324454</url></doc>
